  "title": "輪郭をリストアップ",
  "created": 1781520070,
  "updated": 1781773643,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a2fd6bd3f387a15cc633132",
      "text": "輪郭をリストアップ",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781520070,
      "updated": 1781520070
    },
    {
      "id": "6a33b2640000000000b494fa",
      "text": "[デライト.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781772902,
      "updated": 1781772906
    },
    {
      "id": "6a33b26a0000000000b494fc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781772907,
      "updated": 1781772907
    },
    {
      "id": "6a33b2640000000000b494fb",
      "text": "デライトの特徴のひとつ",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781772902,
      "updated": 1781772936
    },
    {
      "id": "6a33b2760000000000b494fd",
      "text": "複数の輪郭([吹き描き])を並べて表示できる",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781772920,
      "updated": 1781773224
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2fd6c70000000000adecef",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781520073,
      "updated": 1781520073
    },
    {
      "id": "6a33b1540000000000b494f0",
      "text": "デライトのビューはほとんどこれで統一されている",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781772630,
      "updated": 1781772955
    },
    {
      "id": "6a33b1ca0000000000b494f8",
      "text": " 例外は設定画面や説明画面くらい[zatsma.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781772747,
      "updated": 1781772774
    },
    {
      "id": "6a33b1620000000000b494f2",
      "text": " [デライトのタイムライン]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781772644,
      "updated": 1781772649
    },
    {
      "id": "6a33b16a0000000000b494f3",
      "text": " [前景一覧]と[後景一覧]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781772651,
      "updated": 1781772668
    },
    {
      "id": "6a33b17c0000000000b494f4",
      "text": " [デライトの検索]結果",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781772670,
      "updated": 1781772680
    },
    {
      "id": "6a33b23b0000000000b494f9",
      "text": "  検索結果が通常の画面と同じスタイルで表示されるのは嬉しい[zatsma.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781772861,
      "updated": 1781772965
    },
    {
      "id": "6a33b1550000000000b494f1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781772630,
      "updated": 1781772630
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2fd6d80000000000adecf0",
      "text": "全文表示した状態で複数の輪郭を眺めることができる",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781520089,
      "updated": 1781520113
    },
    {
      "id": "6a33b2f60000000000b494ff",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781773048,
      "updated": 1781773048
    },
    {
      "id": "6a33b2fc0000000000b49500",
      "text": "[zatsma.icon]はこれこそデライトとCosenseの大きな違いと考えている",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781773053,
      "updated": 1781773080
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2fd6e00000000000adecf1",
      "text": " [関連ページリスト]に表示されたページの中身を知るには、ページに遷移する必要がある",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781520098,
      "updated": 1781773643
    },
    {
      "id": "6a33b3470000000000b49501",
      "text": " デライトの場合は遷移せずとも内容がわかる",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781773128,
      "updated": 1781773147
    },
    {
      "id": "6a33b2c00000000000b494fe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781772993,
      "updated": 1781772993
    }
  ]
}